sentence: Can I take EECS 270 in Summer 2016 ?
sentence-with-vars: Can I take department0 number0 in Summer 2016 ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( * ) FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 270 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "SU" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
